headline: Citi and SMRT renew 20-year partnership to enhance value for Singapore commuters and consumers
summary: Citi and SMRT are pleased to announce an extension of their partnership to celebrate the start of their 20th year of co-operation, reaffirming a shared commitment to delivering smarter, more rewarding daily journeys for Singapore's commuters.
